    <para>
      <num>D.</num>
      <text>Annuity Allocations. Insofar as annuity considerations are taxable, they shall be allocated by the same method as that adopted for life insurance premiums.</text>
    </para>
    <para>
      <num>E.</num>
      <text>Title Allocations. Title insurance premiums are to be allocated to location of risk.</text>
    </para>
    <para>
      <num>F.</num>
      <text>Federal Areas Allocations. Business done at Army, Navy, or Air Force bases, and other similar federal installations, shall be allocated to the jurisdiction of the insured's residence, as listed on the application.</text>
    </para>
